high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the counter and hang a left, go to the counter on the left that has the knives on it.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the counter, hang a right and go to the fridge that is on the left.
Open the fridge, cut the potato that is in the fridge into slices, close the fridge.
Turn to the left, go to the counter, hang a left, go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn around, go to the counter and hang a right, go to the fridge that is on the left.
Open the fridge, pick up a slice of the potato, close the fridge.
Turn to the left, go to the counter and hang a left, go forward to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the potato when it is done cooking.
Turn around, go to the counter and hang a right, go past the fridge to the garbage can that is on the left.
Put the potato in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked potato in a garbage can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, turn left and take one step then turn left toward the counter.
Pick up the silver knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn right and take two steps, then turn left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and use the knife to cut the potato, then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn left and walk across the room.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside then close the microwave door.
Turn to the right and walk across the room, then turn right and take two steps, then turn left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out a slice of potato, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room.
Open the microwave and place the slice of potato inside to the left of the plate. Turn the microwave on for two seconds, then remove the slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the end of the counter, then turn left to face the trash can.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat up a slice of potato.

high_descs: Walk towards the island counter in the middle
Grab a knife from the island counter
Walk with the knife towards the fridge
Open the fridge slice the potato inside the fridge
Walk with the knife towards the microwave
Put the knife inside the microwave
Walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge and take a slice of the potato
Walk with the slice of potato and put it inside the microwave
Cook the slice of potato and take it out of the microwave
Walk with the slice of the potato towards the trash can next to the fridge
Put the slice of potato inside the trash can
anns.task_desc: Slice the potato inside the fridge, cook a slice in the microwave, put slice of cooked potato in the trash
